{
  "id": "69f195e1108b02ebb4e6df16",
  "title": "個人的な記念日の一覧",
  "created": 1777440230,
  "updated": 1777618659,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69f195e1108b02ebb4e6df16",
      "text": "個人的な記念日の一覧",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777440230,
      "updated": 1777440244
    },
    {
      "id": "69f195f40000000000ff1400",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777440244,
      "updated": 1777440244
    },
    {
      "id": "69f196260000000000ff1403",
      "text": " [誕生日]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777440295,
      "updated": 1777441048
    },
    {
      "id": "69f199180000000000ff140f",
      "text": " [結婚記念日]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777441048,
      "updated": 1777441048
    },
    {
      "id": "69f196460000000000ff1404",
      "text": " [命日]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777440327,
      "updated": 1777440339
    },
    {
      "id": "69f195f40000000000ff1401",
      "text": " 「この味がいいね」と君が言ったから七月六日は[サラダ記念日]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777440245,
      "updated": 1777440292
    },
    {
      "id": "69f195e70000000000ff13ff",
      "text": "\t[自分の井戸端1周年]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777440231,
      "updated": 1777440366
    },
    {
      "id": "69f44c7e0000000000deb437",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777618047,
      "updated": 1777618047
    },
    {
      "id": "69f44c7e0000000000deb438",
      "text": "[atohs.icon]",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777618047,
      "updated": 1777618051
    },
    {
      "id": "69f44c830000000000deb439",
      "text": "　少し前に、「命日」を「記念日」と呼ぶのは違和感がある、というツイートを見た気がする",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777618052,
      "updated": 1777618076
    },
    {
      "id": "69f44c9c0000000000deb43a",
      "text": "　\tAnniversaryだとより許容度が低そう",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777618077,
      "updated": 1777618101
    },
    {
      "id": "69f44cb50000000000deb43b",
      "text": "　\t「記念日」じゃなくて、「◯周年」の話だったかもしれない",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777618101,
      "updated": 1777618118
    },
    {
      "id": "69f44cc50000000000deb43d",
      "text": "　\t\tたとえば、「終戦80周年」とか",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777618118,
      "updated": 1777618139
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1965800000000001fc885",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tこれは大分イヤ[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777440344,
      "updated": 1777618610
    },
    {
      "id": "69f44eb80000000000f16ef8",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t戦後80年とかならよく聞く＋普通に受け入れられるのに",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777618617,
      "updated": 1777618642
    },
    {
      "id": "69f44ed50000000000f16ef9",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t多分祝い事で周年を聞きすぎている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777618646,
      "updated": 1777618659
    },
    {
      "id": "69f44ead0000000000f16ef7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777618605,
      "updated": 1777618605
    }
  ]
}